<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَتَلَاوَمُونَ}</span> ... يَلُومُ بَعْضُهُمْ بَعْضًا عَلَى مَا قَصَدُوهُ مِنْ مَنْعٍ لِلْمَسَاكِينِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَاغِبُونَ}</span> ... طَالِبُونَ الخَيْرَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَذَلِكَ الْعَذَابُ}</span> ... مِثْلَ ذَلِكَ العِقَابِ الَّذِي عَاقَبْنَاهُمْ بِهِ نُعَاقِبُ كُلَّ مَنْ بَخِلَ، وَخَالَفَ أَمْرَ اللهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَخَيَّرُونَ}</span> ... تَشْتَهُونَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَيْمَانٌ}</span> ... عُهُودٌ، وَمَوَاثِيقُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِنَّ لَكُمْ لَمَا تَحْكُمُونَ}</span> ... إِنَّهُ سَيَحْصُلُ لَكُمْ مَا تُرِيدُونَ، وَتَشْتَهُونَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَعِيمٌ}</span> ... كَفِيلٌ وَضَامِنٌ بِأَنْ يَكُونَ لَهُمْ ذَلِكَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُكْشَفُ عَن سَاقٍ}</span> ... يَكْشِفُ رَبُّنَا عَنْ سَاقِهِ؛ فَيَسْجُدُ المُؤْمِنُونَ، وَيَعْجِزُ المُنَافِقُونَ؛ كَمَا ثَبَتَ فِي الحَدِيثِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَاشِعَةً أَبْصَارُهُمْ}</span> ... مُنْكَسِرَةً ذَلِيلَةً؛ لَا يَرْفَعُونَهَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَرْهَقُهُمْ}</span> ... تَغْشَاهُمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَالِمُونَ}</span> ... أَصِحَّاءُ، قَادِرُونَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٤٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْحَدِيثِ}</span> ... القُرْآنِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٤٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَنَسْتَدْرِجُهُم}</span> ... سَنَمُدُّهُمْ بِالأَمْوَالِ وَالنِّعَمِ؛ اسْتِدْرَاجًا لَهُمْ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأُمْلِي لَهُمْ}</span> ... أُمْهِلُهُمْ، وَأُطِيلُ أَعْمَارَهُمْ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَتِينٌ}</span> ... قَوِيٌّ، شَدِيدٌ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>